{
  "2334280": {
    "name": "过木不汪 Stick to the Plan",
    "steam_appid": 2334280,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/c122bdb7fce2f488b83b6ae5a4af5470.avif?t=1744877660\" width=620 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《过木不汪 Stick to the Plan》是一款轻松有趣的解谜游戏，游戏的玩法非常简单：带着你的木棍，避开障碍物，并规划一条通向终点的路径！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/d8edd36f4e687d11d0054d033e26f642.avif?t=1744877660\" width=620 height=135 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/0b621e64225223210c9416680655f5b7.avif?t=1744877660\" width=481 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >操作简单</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过移动、旋转、拾起或放下木棍，就可以完成所有的谜题，<strong>无需任何复杂的操作</strong>，汪汪都可以轻松上手！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/15186836092492cc39d5cbbe0898c81a.poster.avif?t=1744877660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/15186836092492cc39d5cbbe0898c81a.webm?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/15186836092492cc39d5cbbe0898c81a.mp4?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样关卡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发挥你的智慧解决 70 个不重复的关卡谜题</strong>，每个都拥有独特的谜题和不同难度的挑战，你能帮助小狗罗伯特顺利回家吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/cd10ae8dd691e6330383d4e215e60ead.poster.avif?t=1744877660\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/cd10ae8dd691e6330383d4e215e60ead.webm?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/cd10ae8dd691e6330383d4e215e60ead.mp4?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >五种主题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索 5 个不同风格的地区</strong>，每个都拥有自己独特的主题，以及精心设计的纯手绘菜单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/d4b10b094b7c199bce358a1ef1b6a61f.poster.avif?t=1744877660\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/d4b10b094b7c199bce358a1ef1b6a61f.webm?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/d4b10b094b7c199bce358a1ef1b6a61f.mp4?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >视觉辅助</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新增轮廓描绘辅助功能</strong>，让你在任何场景中都能快速找到小狗与它的长棍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/eaa50d215eff9c3c5fa48627754cfc93.poster.avif?t=1744877660\" width=600 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/eaa50d215eff9c3c5fa48627754cfc93.webm?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/eaa50d215eff9c3c5fa48627754cfc93.mp4?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >温馨故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这趟拾棍之旅中，通过一幅幅可爱的手绘插图<strong>发掘小狗罗伯特温馨感人过去</strong>，了解它执着于“完美木棍”背后的真正原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/fd2964614635eb8c2d45b32341fe2274.poster.avif?t=1744877660\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/fd2964614635eb8c2d45b32341fe2274.webm?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334280/extras/fd2964614635eb8c2d45b32341fe2274.mp4?t=1744877660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
